    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p><b>Book of Puzzles</b> Each book contains 10 puzzles made to test the mind and stir the intellect. Solving a single puzzle requires at least an hour and a successful DC 10 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Intelligence</a> check, though every 5 points by which you exceed the check reduces the amount of time you need to solve the puzzle by 10 minutes (to a minimum of 10 minutes to solve an individual puzzle). Once you solve a puzzle, for the next 24 hours you can choose to roll twice on a single <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/disable-device\">Disable Device</a>, <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>, or <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/sense-motive\">Sense Motive</a> skill check and take the higher result. Once all the puzzles are solved, the book is useless, though you can purchase another puzzle <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/books-paper-writing-supplies#TOC-Book\">book</a> with different puzzles. <b>Price</b> 50 gp; <b>Weight</b> 1 lb. <b>Source</b> <a title=\"PZO1129\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/160125671X/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=160125671X&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20&amp;linkId=HSOKQ6X2XAS2GTU6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO1129</a></p>\r\n",
